    },
    "has_children": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "It was so lovely to cook, eat and sleep at home last night. We needed a quiet early one. It’s Saturday morning now, a good sleep under the belt and it’s our last long day of walking on the cards - crazy. It feels like we’ve been on the Camino for years now, time has bent and warped in ways that don’t feel possible. ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "It was so lovely to cook, eat and sleep at home last night. We needed a quiet early one. It’s Saturday morning now, a good sleep under the belt and it’s our last long day of walking on the cards - crazy. It feels like we’ve been on the Camino for years now, time has bent and warped in ways that don’t feel possible. ",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "color": "default"
