    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "We’ve now walked about 200km in two weeks, wow. It’s actually quite incredible. Mostly due to the fact that it doesn’t feel intense or incredibly taxing. Someone needed to write the book ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "We’ve now walked about 200km in two weeks, wow. It’s actually quite incredible. Mostly due to the fact that it doesn’t feel intense or incredibly taxing. Someone needed to write the book ",
          "href": null
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Born to Run",
            "link": {
              "url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6289283-born-to-run"
            }
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "Born to Run",
          "href": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6289283-born-to-run"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": " (great read - definitely read it if you haven’t) in order to convince people that they were as the titled suggests. Yet you really don’t have to write any book to tell me that I’m born to walk. It feels effortless and right. The body can just keep on going forever it seems. ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
