      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "This hotel has one more star than all the others we’ve stayed at - bringing it to a grand total of two ⭐’s. Yet it is noticeable. A big shower and chill on the bed later and we’re refreshed and hungry. We head down to a restaurant for dinner, drink a beer while waiting for the kitchen to open at 7:30pm. Burger, pork tenderloin and too many chips. Then Cait streams the rugby highlights in a fit of patriotic love. ",
            "link": null
